						<li>You must notify us immediately of any unauthorized use of your account</li>
						<li>One account per person is permitted</li>
					</ul>

					<h3>3.2 Gym Code Requirement</h3>
					<ul>
						<li>A valid gym code is required for registration</li>
						<li>Gym codes are provided by authorized gym facilities</li>
						<li>Users can only mark attendance at gyms they are registered with</li>
					</ul>
				</section>

				<section class="legal-section">
					<h2>4. Acceptable Use</h2>
					
					<h3>4.1 Permitted Uses</h3>
					<ul>
						<li>Mark legitimate gym attendance only</li>
						<li>Use workout and nutrition features for personal fitness goals</li>
						<li>Access gym-related information and services</li>
					</ul>

					<h3>4.2 Prohibited Uses</h3>
					<ul>
						<li>Sharing account credentials with others</li>
						<li>Using QR codes fraudulently or for unauthorized attendance</li>
						<li>Attempting to access other users' data</li>
						<li>Reverse engineering or tampering with the App</li>
						<li>Using the App for any illegal or unauthorized purpose</li>
					</ul>
				</section>

				<section class="legal-section">
					<h2>5. QR Code Attendance System</h2>
					
					<h3>5.1 Attendance Marking</h3>
					<ul>
						<li>QR codes must only be scanned at legitimate gym locations</li>
						<li>Attendance records are used for gym management and membership tracking</li>
						<li>False or fraudulent attendance marking may result in account suspension</li>
					</ul>

					<h3>5.2 Data Accuracy</h3>
					<ul>
						<li>While we strive for accuracy, attendance data may occasionally contain errors</li>
						<li>Users should report any discrepancies promptly</li>
						<li>Attendance data does not guarantee gym access or membership validity</li>
					</ul>
				</section>

				<section class="legal-section">
					<h2>6. Membership and Payment Terms</h2>
					
					<h3>6.1 Membership Status</h3>
					<ul>
						<li>Membership status is determined by the gym facility, not the App</li>
						<li>The App displays membership information but does not control access rights</li>
						<li>Payment processing is handled by third-party providers</li>
					</ul>

					<h3>6.2 Subscription and Fees</h3>
					<ul>
						<li>App usage may be subject to gym membership fees</li>
						<li>Payment terms are determined by individual gym facilities</li>
						<li>We are not responsible for membership fee disputes</li>
					</ul>
				</section>

				<section class="legal-section">
					<h2>7. Health and Safety Disclaimers</h2>
					
					<h3>7.1 Medical Disclaimer</h3>
					<ul>
						<li>The App provides general fitness information only</li>
						<li>Workout and nutrition plans are for informational purposes</li>
						<li>Consult healthcare professionals before starting any fitness program</li>
						<li>We are not liable for any health issues or injuries</li>
					</ul>

					<h3>7.2 Fitness Guidance</h3>
