						<li>Stop exercising immediately if you experience discomfort</li>
						<li>The App does not replace professional fitness or medical advice</li>
					</ul>
				</section>

				<section class="legal-section">
					<h2>8. Privacy and Data Protection</h2>
					<p>Your privacy is important to us. Please review our <a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a>, which governs the collection and use of your personal information.</p>
				</section>

				<section class="legal-section">
					<h2>9. Intellectual Property</h2>
					
