					<ul>
						<li>All App content, features, and functionality are owned by us</li>
						<li>You may not copy, modify, or distribute any part of the App</li>
						<li>Trademarks and logos are protected intellectual property</li>
					</ul>

					<h3>9.2 User Content</h3>
