						<li>Service availability may vary by location</li>
						<li>Local laws and regulations apply to App usage</li>
					</ul>
				</section>

				<section class="legal-section">
					<h2>16. Dispute Resolution</h2>
					
					<h3>16.1 Governing Law</h3>
					<ul>
						<li>These Terms are governed by Indian law</li>
						<li>Disputes will be resolved in courts of [Your City], India</li>
					</ul>

